<li><strong>Competitor keyword gaps.</strong> Use Ahrefs or Semrush to find keywords your competitors rank for that you do not.</li>
<li><strong>Review sites (G2, Capterra).</strong> The language buyers use to describe features and frustrations.</li>
<li><strong>Reddit and community forums.</strong> Unfiltered problem descriptions from your target audience.</li>
</ol>
